{"tid":339644,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【集中討論】《香港獨立論》","createTime":"2017-07-29T08:39:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T04:44:54.000Z","uid":92301,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93865afb404e3d46f3b399bda677bb7e7e02d159","tid":339644,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T08:39:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>作者：</strong>梁衍華<br />\n<br />\n<strong>出版社：</strong>香港專業研習學會<br />\n<br />\n<strong>出版日期：</strong>2016年8月<br />\n<br />\n<strong>作者簡介：</strong><br />\n<br />\n梁衍華先生<br />\n香港大學理學士、英國倫敦大學法律學士、紐西蘭律師及大律師<br />\n<br />\n<strong>背景及內容：</strong><br />\n<br />\n不少政客均聲稱主張「香港自決前途」，但住民自決的法理依據為何呢？香港前途為何是730萬人自決而不是14億人決定呢？又如何決定自決的選項呢？另一方面，各選項背後的理據是否已經過詳細討論及研究，而作出選擇的選民又是否清楚理解呢？<br />\n<br />\n雖然「香港獨立」在近年被提出為前途自決選項之一，但也有自決論者認為「一國一制」也可以是選項付諸公投。若果未探討各個選項有否有法理依據及是否合理就貿然投票，有關的決定也不會是一個知情決定 (informed decision)。在此情況下，公投自決的意義成疑，結果也未必明智。<br />\n<br />\n長久以來，香港主權獨立是一個近乎無人觸及的議題。在開始深入探討該議題前，大部份人已經武斷地否定了主權獨立的可能。<strong>本書分為法律篇、古代史篇、近代史篇、當代篇、文化篇及生存篇共六個篇章</strong>，嘗試以學術角度去分析香港主權獨立及相關事項。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法律篇</strong>以國際法角度探討香港主權獨立是否具有法理依據為開端，再揭示有關的法理基礎與香港是否具有獨立歷史及文化的相關性。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>古代史篇及近代史篇</strong>探討香港是否有異於華夏的歷史觀。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>當代篇</strong>則探討因為沒有獨立主權而在當代面對的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>文化篇</strong>探討粵漢文化之別、香港文化異於華夏及粵英混合的特點。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>生存篇</strong>將假設香港作為一個主權獨立國家，將會面對的生存威脅，以及其他國家面對有關威脅時所採取的應對手段。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>購買地點：</strong>開益書店 (or maybe other bookshops in Mong Kok)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>購買網站：</strong><a href=\"http://www.hkaps.com.hk/NewRelease.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkaps.com.hk%2FNewRelease.html&d=gcO4znxt49ZZR8l1uLQ8l57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=12ab59fc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkaps.com.hk/NewRelease.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkaps.com.hk/images/BOOK003_Cover.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkaps.com.hk%2Fimages%2FBOOK003_Cover.jpg&h=da5e9ff3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe3969e462e653e114935212006b19efd63aa6d4","tid":339644,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:17:33.000Z","msg":"- 導正偏頗的（傳統）史觀<br />\n<br />\n- 應把本位放於香港，而非中國大陸"},{"pid":"fd55084db5a7d8c321478ab1c36fa9953405ac15","tid":339644,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:11:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">序言書室每月暢銷書榜（香港獨立論）：</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>二零一六年九月：</strong>第1位<br />\n<strong>十月：</strong>第4位<br />\n<strong>十一月：</strong>第5位<br />\n<strong>二零一七年四月：</strong>第13位<br />\n<strong>六月：</strong>第9位"},{"pid":"0b6597112f610c2c90cca0bc6e4606ef80cf8292","tid":339644,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T11:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/k7v9677nz/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2Fk7v9677nz%2Fimage.jpg&h=2b822a5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFB有條青山派係本民前個PAGE問有多少抄云伯個乜鬼《城邦論》？<br />\n<br />\n班青山柒頭以為自己係天下唯一？<br />\n<br />\n《獨立論》有一段點名屌柒「永續基本法」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96fd719885d40575ab3f0457fcdb9e2ce4b2143","tid":339644,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T12:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/k7v9677nz/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2Fk7v9677nz%2Fimage.jpg&h=2b822a5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFB有條青山派係本民前個PAGE問有多少抄云伯個乜鬼《城邦論》？<br />\n<br />\n班青山柒頭以為自己係天下唯一？<br />\n<br />\n《獨立論》有一段點名屌柒「永續基本法」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係講無退場機制嘅話就唔好胡亂永續基本法"},{"pid":"efc148d70acc8024c9e877f125638b076bda4376","tid":339644,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T12:43:37.000Z","msg":"序言書室每月暢銷書榜（香港獨立論）：<br />\n<br />\n二零一六年<br />\n九月：第1位<br />\n十月：第4位<br />\n十一月：第5位<br />\n二零一七年<br />\n四月：第13位<br />\n六月：第9位<br />\n七月：第12位"},{"pid":"abb3983cb274b0c4bdb791186779b0941cd63e15","tid":339644,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T04:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}